Set Eurostat TOC

Source: R/set_eurostat_toc.R
set_eurostat_toc.Rd

Internal function.

Usage

set_eurostat_toc(lang = "en")

Arguments

lang

2-letter language code, default is "en" (English), other options are "fr" (French) and "de" (German). Used for labeling datasets.

Value

Empty element

see citation("eurostat")
